					<div class="em-hm-fea-pro-block">
						<div class="em-hm-fea-pro-img"><img src="{{section.settings.pro_img | img_url: "original"}}" /></div>
						<h3>RMC-1</h3>
						<h4>16 Channel 9.1.6 Discreet Dolby Atmos & DTS:X Reference Cinema Processor</h4>
						<p>The RMC-1 is a state-of-the-art surround sound processor - designed from the ground up to serve as the nerve center of a modern home theater or surround sound music system. </p>
